WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
ظآزPut every twist behind youظآز

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
ظآزDrift leisurely through timeظآز

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
ظآزMake headway against the windظآز

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
ظآزLet mountains bow to your paceظآز

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 33=

01:44.208 --> 01:45.048
Grandfather,

01:47.447 --> 01:48.367
masters,

01:49.928 --> 01:52.928
and all seniors of Lishan Academy,

01:53.967 --> 01:55.048
I am Mo Xiuyao,

01:56.128 --> 01:57.327
Li's husband.

01:59.008 --> 01:59.928
Thank you all.

02:01.688 --> 02:03.048
I will be good to Li.

02:05.367 --> 02:06.967
I will cherish her with my life.

02:11.808 --> 02:13.128
Thank you for taking care of her.

02:14.808 --> 02:15.607
From now on,

02:17.327 --> 02:19.528
I won't let her be all alone anymore.

02:22.088 --> 02:23.327
You can rest assured.

02:47.767 --> 02:48.767
Come on.

02:48.767 --> 02:49.327
Drink up.

02:49.327 --> 02:51.008
We must drink to our fill today.

02:51.008 --> 02:51.607
Come on.

02:51.607 --> 02:52.568
Thank you all.

02:52.568 --> 02:55.024
- You've worked hard.
- Here, Li.

03:03.387 --> 03:03.887
Alright.

03:03.887 --> 03:04.767
Come on.

03:04.767 --> 03:06.688
Li, nice!

03:07.008 --> 03:09.047
I like this kid.

03:12.167 --> 03:15.408
Manage the household well.
Don't cause him trouble.

03:17.408 --> 03:21.288
I heard he likes fishing. I'll have
a friendly contest with him someday.

03:21.887 --> 03:22.727
Li,

03:25.408 --> 03:30.248
marrying you is a blessing
earned over several lifetimes. Come on.

03:35.848 --> 03:37.368
(When someone suffers a sudden shock,)

03:37.368 --> 03:39.927
like losing a close
family member or friend,

03:39.927 --> 03:42.808
they may find it unbearable
and hallucinate,

03:43.408 --> 03:45.447
seeing them vividly before their eyes

03:45.767 --> 03:47.600
and believing them still alive
and never gone.

06:14.032 --> 06:25.341
(Headmaster Xu's Tomb)

06:47.824 --> 06:51.152
(Master Zhu's Tomb)

07:18.647 --> 07:19.688
(Ye Li's Tomb)
Li.

07:53.008 --> 07:53.808
Yao.

07:56.647 --> 07:57.887
Where did you go?

07:59.847 --> 08:00.847
I went out for a walk.

08:02.967 --> 08:04.447
There are monkeys outside.

08:06.488 --> 08:09.168
It's fine. I'm not afraid of monkeys.

08:15.808 --> 08:17.967
Are you cold? I'll hold you in my arms.

08:29.248 --> 08:30.368
Li, do you know?

08:33.167 --> 08:34.527
I'm actually very afraid of death.

08:38.248 --> 08:39.368
What?

08:40.767 --> 08:41.927
When I was young,

08:42.927 --> 08:44.912
I joined the army
like my father and brother did.

08:46.368 --> 08:52.088
The army prides itself
on bravery and courage.

08:53.608 --> 08:55.328
So I tried to be like
my father and brother,

08:56.047 --> 08:57.248
telling myself,

08:58.088 --> 08:59.167
"You have to be brave.

09:01.008 --> 09:02.488
You fear nothing."

09:05.287 --> 09:07.248
But the first time
I went to the battlefield,

09:10.088 --> 09:11.248
I was so terrified.

09:13.728 --> 09:15.248
I was too scared to move my legs.

09:17.368 --> 09:19.287
Death is truly terrifying.

09:20.287 --> 09:22.807
Buried anywhere
beneath the yellow earth,

09:24.647 --> 09:28.448
consumed by insects and ants,
in complete darkness.

09:31.167 --> 09:32.407
It's truly terrifying.

09:36.848 --> 09:37.767
I'm afraid too.

09:39.767 --> 09:41.527
But now I'm not afraid anymore.

09:44.128 --> 09:45.008
Why?

09:46.767 --> 09:48.008
Because I have you now.

09:53.848 --> 09:55.008
When I think

09:56.887 --> 09:58.407
that as we grow old

09:59.368 --> 10:03.448
and die, we can be buried together,

10:04.927 --> 10:07.527
and I can still hold you like this
even beneath the yellow earth,

10:09.527 --> 10:11.047
I'm not afraid anymore.

10:26.287 --> 10:27.887
Yao, don't be afraid.

10:29.488 --> 10:31.088
I will be with you.

10:36.887 --> 10:37.687
I'm not afraid.

10:39.128 --> 10:40.647
I will be with you too.

10:41.848 --> 10:42.647
So,

10:44.728 --> 10:45.527
Li,

10:47.248 --> 10:48.287
don't be afraid.

10:56.407 --> 10:58.328
I think I'm really drunk.

11:00.208 --> 11:02.407
I probably won't be able
to get up early tomorrow.

11:03.407 --> 11:04.647
Then don't.

11:06.767 --> 11:09.287
But I have so many things to do.

11:11.208 --> 11:12.608
I need to chop firewood.

11:13.527 --> 11:14.767
I can do it.

11:16.008 --> 11:17.488
I need to fetch water.

11:18.687 --> 11:20.128
I can do it too.

11:21.728 --> 11:23.647
I need to dig up bamboo shoots

11:24.488 --> 11:25.807
and cook.

11:27.527 --> 11:28.368
Li.

11:34.128 --> 11:37.407
Why do you always
shoulder everything yourself?

11:41.728 --> 11:43.208
You have me now.

11:45.728 --> 11:47.368
Just sleep well.

11:48.968 --> 11:49.887
Let me

11:52.167 --> 11:53.887
take care of all those things, okay?

12:19.600 --> 12:25.144
ظآزLove is not just romanceظآز

12:25.680 --> 12:30.090
ظآزThey don't get my obsessionظآز

12:30.672 --> 12:35.024
ظآزWhy do two struggling souls make a vowظآز

12:35.024 --> 12:37.808
ظآزAnd stake everythingظآز

12:39.696 --> 12:44.624
ظآزHardship makes us sensibleظآز

12:44.694 --> 12:50.064
ظآزEven with all these feelings,
we hold backظآز

12:50.064 --> 12:53.264
ظآزTo live once more for each otherظآز

12:54.096 --> 12:58.933
ظآزTo become a better version
of ourselvesظآز

12:59.664 --> 13:03.376
ظآزLove has never been just this.
Who knowsظآز

13:03.376 --> 13:05.776
ظآزNobody acknowledges your persistenceظآز

13:05.776 --> 13:08.176
ظآزIf the soul comes with thornsظآز

13:08.176 --> 13:11.423
ظآزEmbrace to feelظآز

13:13.488 --> 13:14.287
You're up.

13:16.567 --> 13:18.488
Did you chop all of this?

13:19.807 --> 13:21.767
Are you hungry? I made you congee.

13:21.767 --> 13:22.267
Come on.

13:22.800 --> 13:26.728
ظآزOn such a long road,
holding hands and never letting goظآز

13:26.728 --> 13:29.608
When I was in the army,
I wasn't very particular about cooking.

13:30.008 --> 13:31.647
I wonder if you like it.

13:34.088 --> 13:34.848
It's good.

13:39.687 --> 13:40.608
Try this.

13:45.008 --> 13:45.968
How's it?

13:50.848 --> 13:54.407
It's a pity I didn't find any mushrooms.
Maybe I was looking in the wrong place.

13:56.448 --> 13:57.608
I know where they are.

13:58.088 --> 14:00.448
After we finish eating,
I'll take you there.

14:00.767 --> 14:01.567
Sure.

14:03.088 --> 14:06.208
After we pick the mushrooms,
I'll fix those doors and windows for you.

14:06.647 --> 14:07.848
And that bed of yours.

14:08.407 --> 14:10.527
I didn't dare
to turn over on it last night,

14:10.848 --> 14:12.728
afraid it would just collapse.

14:15.448 --> 14:16.248
Okay.

14:17.232 --> 14:21.683
ظآزThe little and big things left
in each other's livesظآز

14:22.096 --> 14:26.286
ظآزAlong the way,
we've skipped the explanation of loveظآز

14:26.286 --> 14:29.212
ظآزSeeing a complete lifeظآز

14:29.212 --> 14:34.128
ظآزBecoming mirrors for each otherظآز

14:34.896 --> 14:38.608
ظآزLove has never been just this.
Who knowsظآز

14:38.608 --> 14:40.976
ظآزNobody acknowledges your persistenceظآز

14:40.976 --> 14:43.408
ظآزIf the soul comes with thornsظآز

14:43.408 --> 14:47.024
ظآزEmbrace to feelظآز

14:47.024 --> 14:50.608
ظآزOr the green branch offered as a tutorظآز

14:50.672 --> 14:54.448
ظآزLike friends
always standing side by sideظآز

14:54.448 --> 14:58.064
ظآزLove is but a beginning,
knowing each other day and nightظآز

14:58.064 --> 15:04.208
ظآزOn such a long road,
holding hands and never letting goظآز

15:04.208 --> 15:08.144
ظآزOnly then do we understand why loveظآز

15:08.144 --> 15:13.136
ظآزMeans more than one thingظآز

15:23.472 --> 15:26.927
ظآزLove has never been just this,
I hope you knowظآز

15:26.927 --> 15:27.728
Over there.

15:30.448 --> 15:31.287
Be careful.

15:31.824 --> 15:35.396
ظآزGentleness hides in reserveظآز

15:35.396 --> 15:39.088
ظآزPeacefully supporting
each other in silenceظآز

15:39.088 --> 15:42.736
ظآزSo intimate
that we constantly feel insecureظآز

15:42.768 --> 15:46.456
ظآزLove is but a beginning,
the pain is briefظآز

15:46.456 --> 15:52.944
ظآزOn such a long road,
I hold your fingersظآز

15:52.944 --> 16:05.741
ظآزI haven't gotten it off my chestظآز

16:08.328 --> 16:10.647
Is the moon
on Lishan Mountain beautiful?

16:11.047 --> 16:12.592
Different from what you usually see.

16:14.968 --> 16:18.887
It seems so close, as if I could
touch its light just by reaching out.

16:34.807 --> 16:38.167
(Over these years,
it accompanied you for many nights,)

16:38.767 --> 16:40.767
(also witnessed
many moments of your loneliness.)

16:41.407 --> 16:44.208
(From now on,
as the moon rises and sets,)

16:44.968 --> 16:47.567
(I will always be with you, Li.)

16:50.968 --> 16:52.248
(Suixue Pass)
Fabrics on sale!

16:52.368 --> 16:53.167
Take a look!

16:53.167 --> 16:54.128
Come take a look!

16:57.927 --> 16:58.887
Come and see!

16:58.887 --> 16:59.687
Fabrics on sale!

16:59.728 --> 17:00.687
Come and see!

17:01.208 --> 17:02.008
On sale!

17:02.128 --> 17:05.728
I heard this was a place of bitter cold,
short of food and clothes.

17:06.168 --> 17:09.607
But after years of ceasefire
and trade between the two nations,

17:10.047 --> 17:12.327
it looks pretty prosperous now.

17:13.287 --> 17:16.728
This is also what Lingyun wanted.
It's a pity she couldn't see it.

17:17.928 --> 17:20.248
My lord, let's get some food.

17:38.047 --> 17:42.127
My Lord, at your age,
you would've let go long ago if you could.

17:43.847 --> 17:45.448
I've let go, anyway.

17:46.767 --> 17:48.127
Who cares?

17:50.047 --> 17:51.087
Coming.

17:53.367 --> 17:54.127
Excuse me.

17:54.127 --> 17:54.928
Here's your meal.

17:55.127 --> 17:56.888
One bowl of broth
and half a steamed cake.

17:56.888 --> 17:58.127
Got it, coming right up!

17:58.367 --> 18:01.448
My lord, is that the young clerk
from Shende Shop?

18:01.488 --> 18:03.168
The one got imprisoned
with Princess Ding.

18:03.248 --> 18:04.728
I've seen him several times before.

18:13.287 --> 18:14.127
Han Mingxi?

18:15.888 --> 18:16.728
Master Feng.

18:17.087 --> 18:17.888
Have a seat.

18:20.527 --> 18:22.087
Why are you at Suixue Pass?

18:22.327 --> 18:23.760
Not working at Shende Shop anymore?

18:23.888 --> 18:25.448
Did Princess Ding treat you badly?

18:26.047 --> 18:28.607
Not at all. Ye Li treated me very well.

18:31.567 --> 18:33.200
I came with my family for some business.

18:33.767 --> 18:34.968
Why are you here too?

18:36.168 --> 18:39.408
I brought my beloved back
to visit her hometown.

18:39.888 --> 18:41.527
You got married?

18:43.888 --> 18:46.367
I heard people saying
that despite your age

18:46.567 --> 18:49.248
and your wealth,
you still wouldn't marry

18:50.087 --> 18:51.688
because you had some hidden ailment.

18:51.847 --> 18:54.928
Nonsense! Don't spread rumors.

18:55.607 --> 18:56.968
Which lady did you marry?

18:58.208 --> 18:59.767
Princess Lingyun of Cangbei.

19:01.408 --> 19:02.208
But...

19:04.728 --> 19:05.527
But she...

19:05.928 --> 19:06.728
Yes.

19:08.287 --> 19:09.968
But people here won't forget her.

19:10.888 --> 19:11.767
Neither will I.

19:14.607 --> 19:15.527
Master Feng,

19:17.248 --> 19:18.047
my condolences.

19:20.968 --> 19:22.168
How long have you been here?

19:22.607 --> 19:25.248
What happened to Su Zuidie
after she was brought back to Cangbei?

19:26.448 --> 19:27.448
Was she executed?

19:39.327 --> 19:41.688
No, I haven't heard about it.

19:43.248 --> 19:44.047
Probably,

19:45.567 --> 19:46.888
she died quite miserably.

19:58.480 --> 20:01.982
(Carving and Painting)

20:15.047 --> 20:18.008
Even painters from Dachu
come to Suixue Pass to make a living.

20:20.807 --> 20:22.127
Let's find an inn first.

20:22.508 --> 20:23.008
Okay.

20:23.008 --> 20:23.527
Let's go.

20:40.968 --> 20:42.127
Ran away?

20:42.127 --> 20:44.888
Yes, at least five or six years ago.

20:45.287 --> 20:47.888
The mountain doesn't seem
to be inhabited for a long time.

20:48.767 --> 20:49.928
How can you tell

20:49.928 --> 20:50.888
that they ran away?

20:51.367 --> 20:53.408
I sent people to search carefully.

20:53.688 --> 20:56.008
All the rooms
on Lishan Mountain are empty.

20:56.127 --> 20:57.448
The land has long been abandoned.

20:57.888 --> 20:59.728
There are barely
any decent clothes left.

20:59.728 --> 21:03.127
There's only Princess Ding
in the entire Lishan Academy.

21:03.127 --> 21:05.767
But when we questioned her,
she couldn't answer.

21:06.047 --> 21:09.527
I thought this was a grave matter,
so I rushed back to report to you.

21:11.527 --> 21:13.408
Gongshu Yang, what do you think?

21:16.607 --> 21:19.127
I think this is a bit strange.

21:19.248 --> 21:22.758
Given Xu Qingyun's character,
it's unlikely he would request

21:22.758 --> 21:25.287
to seal the mountain
and then secretly flee.

21:25.688 --> 21:26.807
It's hard to say.

21:27.127 --> 21:31.008
Over time, no one can endure
the harsh life on the mountain.

21:31.047 --> 21:34.208
Maybe they just ran away
along some path.

21:39.567 --> 21:41.208
Mother!

21:45.607 --> 21:46.168
Mother.

21:50.008 --> 21:51.448
Another report from Prince Ding.

21:51.807 --> 21:53.457
It says that apart from Princess Ding,

21:53.457 --> 21:55.327
everyone on Lishan Mountain
died of illness.

21:58.008 --> 21:58.807
Died of illness?

22:01.127 --> 22:02.448
It happened a few years ago.

22:04.080 --> 22:09.136
(Everyone except Princess Ding is dead)

22:12.767 --> 22:13.567
Gongshu Yang.

22:15.767 --> 22:16.567
Here.

22:18.327 --> 22:20.687
I appoint you as the Secret Investigator
of Lishan Mountain,

22:20.687 --> 22:22.128
acting under the emperor's orders.

22:22.527 --> 22:24.688
Depart immediately for Lishan Mountain

22:24.688 --> 22:25.888
to find out the truth.

22:26.928 --> 22:28.248
I obey your decree.

22:39.367 --> 22:42.527
Li, come on.

22:49.688 --> 22:52.327
From now on,
you can sit here to watch the moon.

22:52.728 --> 22:53.527
Try it.

23:00.648 --> 23:01.327
Comfortable?

23:26.985 --> 23:33.136
(Lishan Academy)

24:08.648 --> 24:11.567
Li, sit and rest for a bit.

24:14.767 --> 24:17.888
What's going on outside?
It sounds quite noisy.

24:22.567 --> 24:25.287
The Emperor sent Gongshu Yang here
with a guard of honor

24:25.648 --> 24:26.807
to pay respects.

24:27.567 --> 24:30.607
So suddenly? Has the date been set?

24:32.287 --> 24:33.807
I told them to come two days later.

24:38.767 --> 24:40.408
Do you have things to do tomorrow?

24:43.928 --> 24:44.728
No.

24:45.888 --> 24:48.928
Look, you've picked
a whole basket of bamboo shoots.

24:50.248 --> 24:53.047
You've chopped the firewood,
copied the books,

24:53.888 --> 24:55.847
and even fixed the windows for me.

24:56.327 --> 24:57.847
What else is there for me to do?

25:00.127 --> 25:01.607
Watch the sunrise with me tomorrow.

25:02.928 --> 25:03.448
Sure.

25:04.567 --> 25:07.607
I know the best place
to watch the sunrise.

25:08.488 --> 25:09.567
The scenery is beautiful.

25:10.127 --> 25:15.008
As if you can hold the sun in your palm
just by reaching out.

25:46.047 --> 25:47.327
We are too early.

25:48.567 --> 25:52.648
It's still dark,
and it'll be a long wait until sunrise.

25:56.847 --> 25:57.648
A shooting star!

26:00.127 --> 26:00.928
Where is it?

26:01.688 --> 26:03.408
There, it fell.

26:08.527 --> 26:09.327
Another one!

26:18.648 --> 26:19.728
You're teasing me.

26:20.807 --> 26:22.047
I really saw them.

26:26.488 --> 26:27.648
Then I won't sleep.

26:28.287 --> 26:31.127
I'll keep my eyes open
and see if there are shooting stars.

26:35.527 --> 26:36.488
What do you see?

26:38.008 --> 26:41.567
It's pitch black. I can't see anything.

26:43.688 --> 26:44.648
How can that be?

26:47.488 --> 26:51.448
Although it's dark,
there's still plenty to see.

26:52.968 --> 26:57.127
Look at the stars. There are only a few,
yet they are still bright.

26:59.047 --> 27:02.087
The clouds at night
are also very special.

27:02.287 --> 27:03.607
Grayish purple, like bruises,

27:04.688 --> 27:08.327
also like the waves of the deep sea,
up in the firmament,

27:09.208 --> 27:11.928
surging and stacking in layers.

27:15.767 --> 27:19.367
I think you should quit your job
at Jingzhao Prefecture.

27:20.168 --> 27:23.248
With your imagination,
you should be a storybook writer.

27:25.847 --> 27:28.527
You can't see because you don't want to.

27:32.047 --> 27:33.488
At midnight, we long for dawn,

27:33.888 --> 27:36.087
and at dawn,
we wait for the moon to rise.

27:36.448 --> 27:41.728
But the scenery at every moment
is worth appreciating.

27:45.807 --> 27:47.527
Just like the ups and downs in life,

27:48.327 --> 27:51.968
whether acceptable or not,
you can't skip over them.

27:52.928 --> 27:54.208
You have to face them

27:55.767 --> 27:56.807
and overcome them.

27:58.648 --> 28:01.208
Once you overcome them, new scenery

28:02.208 --> 28:03.047
and a new life await.

28:12.488 --> 28:14.168
We're just watching the sunrise.

28:15.208 --> 28:16.527
Why so many deep thoughts?

28:18.728 --> 28:19.527
Mo Xiuyao,

28:20.928 --> 28:22.208
you're only in your twenties.

28:23.047 --> 28:25.168
You're not a nagging old man.

28:26.367 --> 28:27.168
Fine.

28:28.408 --> 28:29.527
Let's watch the sunrise.

28:39.488 --> 28:42.847
The clouds are very thick today.
I'm afraid we won't see the sunrise.

28:46.008 --> 28:48.527
Then come with me to another place.

28:49.527 --> 28:50.367
Where to?

28:56.847 --> 28:57.688
Li,

29:00.127 --> 29:04.008
do you remember
what I told you that night?

29:06.728 --> 29:09.767
You've said so many things. Which one?

29:11.527 --> 29:13.047
No matter what happens,

29:14.688 --> 29:16.807
I will always be with you.

29:18.087 --> 29:18.888
So,

29:20.688 --> 29:21.807
don't be afraid.

29:24.087 --> 29:25.448
Always move forward.

29:29.408 --> 29:32.047
With you here, I'm not afraid.

30:07.928 --> 30:11.888
Wild monkeys often roam
the back mountain.

30:12.008 --> 30:13.728
They are fierce.

30:13.847 --> 30:16.928
Don't come here anymore.

30:21.728 --> 30:22.527
What's wrong?

30:22.527 --> 30:26.728
Grandfather said there are monkeys
on the back mountain. We can't go there.

30:27.928 --> 30:31.367
There are monkeys
over there. Lots of them.

30:31.807 --> 30:34.648
Don't be afraid, Li. I'm here.

30:38.168 --> 30:39.087
Don't be afraid.

30:41.168 --> 30:42.008
I'm here.

30:58.648 --> 30:59.567
Don't be afraid, Li.

31:01.287 --> 31:03.127
Let's go. It's okay.

31:22.008 --> 31:24.367
It's okay. Don't be afraid.
There are no monkeys.

31:29.847 --> 31:31.287
Don't be afraid.

31:42.488 --> 31:45.008
It's okay.

31:58.367 --> 31:59.248
Li,

32:00.888 --> 32:01.847
are you alright?

32:11.047 --> 32:11.928
Let's go.

32:39.501 --> 32:41.296
(Headmaster Xu's Tomb)

33:10.256 --> 33:13.392
(Headmaster Xu's Tomb)

34:07.527 --> 34:09.647
Sir, we've gathered the herbs.

34:12.247 --> 34:13.047
Sir.

34:15.127 --> 34:16.928
Is this all the herbs?

34:17.328 --> 34:20.488
This is all we can find.
We've searched the entire mountain.

34:21.527 --> 34:23.207
Sir, are you alright?

34:23.207 --> 34:26.448
Stay back! Don't come close!

34:26.808 --> 34:27.727
Get out of here!

34:28.247 --> 34:31.207
Li, it's too dangerous here.
Get out of here.

34:31.207 --> 34:32.527
Get out of here.

34:32.527 --> 34:33.247
- Master.
- Go.

34:33.247 --> 34:35.247
Let me in. I can take care of you.

34:35.288 --> 34:36.408
Get out of here.

34:36.647 --> 34:39.607
Terrible! Headmaster is dying!

34:42.127 --> 34:43.047
My lady.

34:44.888 --> 34:45.488
My lady.

34:45.488 --> 34:46.567
It's useless.

34:47.727 --> 34:49.288
It's useless.

34:51.247 --> 34:53.567
Grandfather!

34:56.808 --> 34:59.448
Grandfather!

35:02.647 --> 35:03.607
How are you feeling?

35:09.127 --> 35:10.768
Go! Get out of here!

35:11.167 --> 35:13.167
Get out of here!

35:16.008 --> 35:18.727
No way.

35:19.527 --> 35:20.527
Where are you going?

35:21.727 --> 35:24.288
I'm going down the mountain
and find a physician.

35:24.288 --> 35:25.288
Find soldiers, medicine,

35:25.288 --> 35:26.647
and someone who can save them.

35:26.647 --> 35:28.687
- Qingshuang, take care of Grandfather.
- Come back here.

35:30.127 --> 35:31.087
Come back.

35:37.647 --> 35:38.527
Li, come back.

35:43.488 --> 35:44.207
Li!

35:44.247 --> 35:44.968
Li!

35:47.647 --> 35:48.567
Li!

35:54.408 --> 35:55.127
Go over there.

35:59.687 --> 36:00.408
Help!

36:00.468 --> 36:00.968
Li.

36:00.968 --> 36:01.647
Help!

36:02.288 --> 36:03.848
I'm sorry. I don't want to hurt you.

36:03.848 --> 36:04.808
But you can't do so.

36:05.227 --> 36:05.727
Let me go!

36:05.727 --> 36:06.928
- Go!
- Let go!

36:06.928 --> 36:07.647
Go!

36:11.008 --> 36:11.888
Shut the door.

36:16.727 --> 36:19.527
Open the door! Senior, open the door!

36:19.968 --> 36:21.687
Or it'll be too late! Open it!

36:21.768 --> 36:22.888
Li,

36:24.448 --> 36:26.320
Lishan was sealed
not for selfish interests,

36:26.607 --> 36:28.304
but to uphold justice in this world,

36:28.607 --> 36:31.488
and to resist the treacherous act
of Guo Jin usurping the throne.

36:37.727 --> 36:41.808
Li, if we go down the mountain
to seek help now,

36:42.328 --> 36:43.848
it'd be bowing to the rebels,

36:44.207 --> 36:47.527
betraying Headmaster's
lifelong reputation,

36:48.047 --> 36:49.928
and bringing shame to Lishan Mountain.

36:50.607 --> 36:53.928
If everyone is dead,
what use is an empty reputation?

36:54.888 --> 36:56.808
I just want my grandfather to live.

36:57.647 --> 36:59.928
I just want masters and seniors to live.

36:59.928 --> 37:02.687
Open the door now! Open it!

37:03.207 --> 37:04.687
Let me out!

37:08.527 --> 37:11.527
Master Helai. He will save us.

37:13.087 --> 37:14.727
He has superb medical skills.

37:16.087 --> 37:17.207
Li, trust me.

37:18.488 --> 37:19.727
This is just an epidemic.

37:20.448 --> 37:23.328
Everything will be fine.

37:23.607 --> 37:24.527
It will.

37:25.008 --> 37:27.408
Senior, you don't understand.

37:28.087 --> 37:31.047
We are out of medicine now.
We're out of medicine.

37:31.047 --> 37:33.527
Open the door now. I beg you.

37:33.848 --> 37:36.567
Senior!

37:37.687 --> 37:39.448
Open the door!

37:41.328 --> 37:43.607
I'm begging you!

37:47.288 --> 37:48.167
My lady.

37:49.328 --> 37:50.368
My lady.

37:52.087 --> 37:52.968
My lady.

37:53.408 --> 37:54.288
Qingshuang.

37:56.408 --> 37:57.247
Qingshuang.

37:59.488 --> 38:00.368
My lady.

38:03.488 --> 38:04.288
My lady.

38:04.567 --> 38:05.368
Qingshuang.

38:06.488 --> 38:08.888
How are Grandfather and the others?

38:09.408 --> 38:13.247
Headmaster... Headmaster
seems to have fallen asleep.

38:13.448 --> 38:17.488
Master Helai won't let us in,
and he won't open the door.

38:19.008 --> 38:22.368
But more and more people
are getting sick.

38:26.567 --> 38:29.768
Qingshuang, what's wrong?
Are you alright?

38:31.408 --> 38:34.928
I'm fine, my lady.

38:35.607 --> 38:38.408
I-I'm just scared.

38:40.087 --> 38:42.047
Qingshuang, don't be scared.

38:42.768 --> 38:45.247
You go down the mountain
and find the soldiers.

38:45.888 --> 38:47.008
Tell them

38:47.687 --> 38:50.247
if anything happens to us,
they will be held accountable.

38:51.288 --> 38:52.247
My lady,

38:55.247 --> 38:56.448
I'm scared.

38:57.167 --> 38:59.247
Qingshuang, don't be scared.

38:59.888 --> 39:02.288
Go down the mountain now. Just do it.

39:02.647 --> 39:03.848
Okay.

39:07.247 --> 39:08.087
I'll go.

39:15.488 --> 39:18.167
Qingshuang, have you gone?

39:19.167 --> 39:19.968
Qingshuang?

39:23.567 --> 39:24.368
Qingshuang?

39:30.127 --> 39:32.008
Qingshuang, step away from the window.

39:44.607 --> 39:45.408
Qingshuang!

39:51.368 --> 39:52.848
Qingshuang, how are you?

39:53.127 --> 39:55.047
Hang on. I'll find someone to help.

40:10.727 --> 40:12.928
Senior.

40:31.207 --> 40:32.167
Master Helai.

40:32.488 --> 40:35.087
Get out of here!

40:38.247 --> 40:40.888
Master Helai!

40:46.047 --> 40:48.167
Master Zhu!

40:48.968 --> 40:49.848
Master Yu!

41:01.888 --> 41:02.768
Grandfather.

41:40.408 --> 41:41.127
Grandfather.

41:42.527 --> 41:43.687
Grandfather.

41:49.247 --> 41:50.527
Grandfather.

41:53.167 --> 41:54.047
Grand...

41:57.888 --> 41:59.527
Don't leave me.

42:41.552 --> 42:44.304
(Preview)

42:45.408 --> 42:47.207
There were four of these straw dolls.

42:47.888 --> 42:49.127
Lu Changfu,

42:49.768 --> 42:50.727
the Ye family,

42:51.288 --> 42:52.448
Marquis Muyang,

42:52.968 --> 42:54.047
and the fourth one...

42:55.368 --> 42:58.628
- Empress Dowager.
- Marquis Muyang framed loyal subjects

42:58.628 --> 42:59.768
and abused torture.

42:59.768 --> 43:03.687
Without her approval and indulgence,
how could he be so rampant?

43:04.127 --> 43:07.207
And she is still
the mighty Empress Dowager.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
ظآزBoth joy and grief
make the trip worthwhileظآز

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
ظآزTrying to catch up
to your own lost shadowظآز

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
ظآزWithin the wilds, echoes thriveظآز

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
ظآزClear mind leads to a clear pathظآز

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
ظآزBe grateful to your lossesظآز

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
ظآزMake your steps weightlessظآز

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
ظآزPut every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through timeظآز

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
ظآزMake headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your paceظآز

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
ظآزUnbound by formظآز

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
ظآزUnbound by formظآز
